%20did%20surprisingly%20well.%20When%20I%20asked%20for%20a%20short%2C%20professional%20email%2C%20the%20chatbot%20gave%20me%20a%20quick%20three-sentence%20refrain.%20When%20I%20asked%20for%20a%20longer%2C%20more%20thoughtful%20email%2C%20it%20gave%20me%20solid%2C%20bland%20copy.%20I%20sent%20the%20shorter%20copy%20with%20some%20minor%20edits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20fellow%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20we%20sometimes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20networking%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20other%20employees%20in%20our%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecohort.%20This%20week%2C%20we%20met%20after%20work%20to%20sip%20mimosas%20and%20talk%20about%20our%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20ChatGPT%20make%20me%20friends%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20ChatGPT%20applauded%20that%20I%20took%20the%20first%20step%20to%20%26quot%3Bshow%20up.%26quot%3B%20It%20gave%20me%20some%20basic%20principles%2C%20like%20being%20curious%20and%20not%20talking%20to%20any%20one%20person%20for%20too%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20suggested%20some%20things%20to%20talk%20about%20based%20on%20our%20past%20conversations%3A%20My%20time%20in%20Boston%2C%20my%20coverage%20of%20consumer%20tech%2C%20my%20love%20of%20reality%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pushed%20back%3A%20I've%20met%20the%20fellows%20before%2C%20and%20don't%20need%20basic%20advice%20to%20avoid%20awkwardness.%20How%20should%20we%20deepen%20our%20bond%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20ChatGPT%20told%20me%20to%20peel%20off%20for%20one-on-one%20moments%2C%20and%20to%20ask%20more%20personal%2C%20reflective%20questions.%20The%20chatbot%20also%20pushed%20me%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20the%20first%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20inviting%20people%20out%20for%20a%20coffee%20or%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tips%2C%20like%20most%20of%20ChatGPT's%20advice%20throughout%20the%20week%2C%20were%20bland.%20But%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20remin