20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20this%20is%20becoming%20less%20distinct%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20kind%20of%20coming%20together%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20hottest%20listing%20of%20the%20year%2C%20Figma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-donation-440-million-marin-community-foundation-evan-wallace-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewent%20public%20on%20July%2031%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20%2419.3%20billion%20valuation%2C%20three%20years%20after%20Adobe%20was%20set%20to%20acquire%20the%20design%20software%20startup%20for%20almost%20the%20same%20amount.%20By%20market%20close%20that%20day%2C%20Figma's%20stock%20had%20more%20than%20tripled%20its%20initial%20public%20offering%20price%2C%20valuing%20the%20company%20at%20nearly%20%2468%20billion%2C%20giving%20its%20Silicon%20Valley%20investors%20a%20big%20payday.%20It%20brought%20to%20an%20end%20a%20three-year%20tech%20IPO%20dry%20spell%2C%20and%20the%20company%20threw%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-party-wall-street-photos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emassive%20block%20party%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20front%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20valuation%20has%20since%20slid%20to%20%2438%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20YC%20talk%2C%20Field%20also%20said%20designers%20would%20become%20more%20important%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20if%20you%20really%20believe%20that%20development%20gets%20easier%20and%20it's%20more%20simple%20to%20create%20software%2C%20it's%20faster%20to%20create%20software.%20Then%20what%20is%20your%20differentiator%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20design%2C%20it's%20craft%2C%20it's%20attention%20to%20detail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EField%20added%20that%20designers%20will%20have%20more%20leverage%20in%20the%20future%20and%20more%20will%20step%20into%20founder%20and%20