ts%20that%20distinguishing%20the%20stigma%20of%20female%20flowers%20from%20the%20pollen%20of%20male%20florets%20was%20a%20difficult%20task%20initially.%20Later%2C%20he%20adopted%20the%20hand-pollination%20method%20since%20natural%20pollination%20was%20not%20effective.%20This%20method%2C%20involving%20the%20delicate%20brushing%20of%20each%20petal%2C%20consumed%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20experimented%20on%20several%20plants.%20Nothing%20worked%20for%20the%20first%20three%20to%20four%20years.%20One%20evening%2C%20I%20noticed%20flower%20buds%20and%20hoped%20they%20would%20turn%20into%20fruit.%20About%20seven%20to%20eight%20months%20later%2C%20I%20was%20overjoyed%20to%20see%20my%20efforts%20bear%20fruit.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20named%20the%20variety%20yet.%20As%20long%20as%20it%20gives%20me%20a%20good%20yield%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2070-year-old%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECross-pollination%20vs%20natural%20pollination%3A%20Expert%20insights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nitai%20Mudi%2C%20Senior%20Scientist%20at%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(Agriculture%20Science%20Centre)%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCross-pollination%20is%20a%20common%20practice.%20However%2C%20hybrid%20varieties%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20produce%20viable%20seeds%20for%20future%20use.%20The%20best%20results%20often%20come%20from%20natural%20pollination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20District%20Horticulture%20Officer%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%20due%20to%20protocol%2C%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20horticulture%20department%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20conduct%20fruit%20variety%20identification.%20That%20can%20only%20be%20done%20through%20gene%20testing%20or%20tissue%20culture%20at%20specialised%20labs%20like%20Bidhan%20Chandra%20Krishi%20Viswavidyalaya%20in%20Kalyani.%20But%20most%20farmers%20avoid%20this%20due%20to%20high%20costs%20and%20are%20content%20with%20a%20good%20harvest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20fruitful%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20Halder%20focused%20on%20preserving%20this%20resilient%20breed.%20To%20scale%20up%2C%20he%20bought%20two%20more%20bighas%20of%20land%20and%20planted%201%2C200%2C%20500%2C%20and%20175%20papaya%20plants%20in%20three%20separate%20fields.%20Since%201986%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20turning%20a%20steady%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPapaya%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3ECarica%20papaya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F475953%2Ffarmer-innovator-golden-sitaphal-custard-apple-navnath-kaspate-maharashtra-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20varieties%20in%20West%20Bengal%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincluding%20Ranchi%20Selection%2C%20Honeydew%2C%20Washington%2C%20and%20Coorg%20Green.%20However%2C%20most%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20disease%20and%20sensitive%20to%20soil%20and%20climate.%20Halder%E2%80%99s%20unnamed%20variety%20is%20disease-resistant%20and%20high-yielding.%20Each%20plant%20produces%20around%2040%20kilos%20of%20fruit%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-8_11zon-1754545353.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20papaya%20variety%20by%20Bengal%20farmer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-8_11zon-1754545353.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-8_11zon-1754545353-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-8_11zon-1754545353-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-8_11zon-1754545353-768x402.jp