(amazing).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20street%20food%20sees%20a%20capricious%20dynamic.%20Light%20eats%20are%20interspersed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261268%2Fbiryani-map-of-india-taste-the-history-find-your-favourite-among-28-versions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheavy%20%3Cem%3Ebiryanis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(aromatic%20rice%20cooked%20with%20meats)%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20then%20there%20are%20the%20foods%20whose%20arrival%20on%20the%20plates%20is%20prequelled%20by%20as%20compelling%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20long%20%3Cem%3Echirey.%20%3C%2Fem%3EOne%20of%20Old%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20best%20vegetarian%20street%20snacks%2C%20the%20name%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20slender%20shape%20that%20resembles%20little%20birds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20made%20from%20a%20mix%20of%20gram%20flour%20and%20ground%20lentils%3B%20the%20batter%20is%20seasoned%20with%20green%20chillies%2C%20onions%2C%20and%20herbs%20before%20being%20shaped%20around%20thin%20skewers%20and%20grilled%20over%20open%20coals.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20beautifully%20curved%20fritter%20with%20a%20smoky%20crust%20and%20a%20tender%2C%20cakey%20inside.%20Long%20%3Cem%3Echirey%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20once%20sold%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abu%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDJEtrSyy3K0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDJEtrSyy3K0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv