d%20in%20water%20or%20spiced%20brine)%3B%20the%20white%20%3Cem%3Ephulke%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabsorb%20salted%20water%2C%20becoming%20soft%20and%20airy%2C%20while%20the%20red%20ones%20soak%20in%20a%20chilli-spiked%2C%20tangy%20liquid%20that%20gives%20them%20a%20fermented%20zing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20have%20found%20favour%20in%20Fatma%20Laiba%20(20)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20loyalist%20at%20Abu%E2%80%99s%20walks.%20When%20Fatma%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20in%202022%20to%20pursue%20a%20degree%20in%20sociology%2C%20she%20had%20a%20fair%20picture%20of%20the%20Sufi-ism%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edargah%20%3C%2Fem%3E(shrine)%20culture%20and%20the%20most%20popular%20spots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20Abu%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eintroduced%20me%20to%20some%20really%20niche%20places%20of%20Old%20Delhi%2C%20little-known%20streets%20and%20of%20course%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231449%2Fgoogle-samosa-entrepreneur-bohri-food-dawoodi-bohra-nalli-nihari-chicken-biryani-traditional-recipes-mumbai-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Enalli%20nihari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mutton%20stew)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Edori%20kebabs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20When%20Fatma%20would%20go%20on%20these%20walks%20and%20later%20talk%20about%20everything%20she%20had%20learnt%2C%20in%20her%20circle%20of%20Gen%20Z%20friends%2C%20they%20would%20be%20compelled%20to%20enquire%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20always%20intrigued%20by%20the%20workshops%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20or%20the%20new%20places%20I%20was%20seeing%20on%20these%20walks.%20They%20would%20ask%20to%20come%20along%2C%20and%20they%20did.%20They%20would%20love%20everything%20they%20learnt%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20of%20the%20presentation%20that%20Abu%20relies%20on.%20The%20content%20appeals%20to%20anyone%20interested%20in%20history%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20senior%20citizen%20or%20a%20youngster%2C